Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.44,Karaoke Translation op,....TEXT....,0,0,446,,{\a6\pos(499.5,486)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Comandante da Battle 7, Maximilian Jenius
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.89,Karaoke Translation op,....TEXT....,0,0,459,,{\a6\pos(492,499.5)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Mylene F. Jenius
